#!/bin/sh

cat <<EOF
This is a STI base image responsible for consuming a Java/Maven
and deploying it onto the targete application container.
To use it, install STI: https://github.com/openshift/source-to-image.

Details:
If a pom.xml is present in the source directory, the project is built with maven and the
output in target will be copied into the /opt/jboss/deploy directory.
EOF
